{"tid":1063896,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港700中學生罷課","createTime":"2019-03-16T06:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T07:08:01.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f302da885a5c45fc3797002a36395e12ac3fda88","tid":1063896,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/956665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F956665&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnAgLKV3biakQup4fopcqKIo%3D&h=deb4465d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F956665&h=99eb873b\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/956665</a><br />\n<br />\n由瑞典一名女學生發起的罷課今早舉行，本港有近700名中學生響應，在中環遮打花園集合，並遊行到政府總部。召集人之一的Zara認為是次活動是好開始，期望政府可作出行動面對全球暖化問題，並增加香港可再生能源的比率。<br />\n<br />\n大部分出席活動均是國際學校學生，亦有個別本地學生到場支持，就讀九龍華仁書院的中六學生李淳希獲發起組織邀請到場演講，他表示，自己是應屆文憑試考生，都專程到場支持，他知道很多家長不讓學生出席，但認為幾個小時的活動對學習無影響。<br />\n<br />\n另一位就讀本地學校中五的卓同學則特意請假到場支持。她認為香港回收方面十分落後，亦指政府應提升社會的環保意識，如推行更多源頭減廢政策。"},{"pid":"07c0514142b89f88005457b91c53aca8c4446be6","tid":1063896,"uid":84355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:31:39.000Z","msg":"要重刷，不了"},{"pid":"1d65adedc4a38e068d5868b3fe29ef1625aaa3d3","tid":1063896,"uid":175808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"請假都算罷課咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07191f152f3f3bdcb371db33dfe6564a013038b5","tid":1063896,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"打工仔星期日罷工添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb969da5096c7adec6fa62d1873361ae72f52561","tid":1063896,"uid":211579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T06:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06